| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3742 — Recovery Inhibition (rhysida)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3dc9ee46-0b58-5df0-8d95-dfa85ffb0eae"
